  "dct_description_sm": [
    "NJ Rail Roads is a line theme representing public and private rail lines in New Jersey. Attribute information includes line name, directional code and agency of administration. Data is derived from files from the New Jersey Port Authority with a source scale of 1:100,000. These data were projected for use with the Community Cartography New York City datasets and an accompanying point file of New Jersey rail stations."
